like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"已考水喉中工<br />\n遲D學揸巴士<br />\n可能會學驗樓，揸鏟車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f24a55f38c5442d72e73a91c339c0eaf18001e","tid":2496830,"uid":92363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e4f8ad840d134bc3ac13a666f3da73c658840be","tid":2496830,"uid":122134,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"通渠, <br />\n佢地無人肯做<br />\n利申 通緊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"好唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b28e8a632823076e28f06004d5d71f356c16109","tid":2496830,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bdf420273e1fd595219866e059a3c15cf15f288","tid":2496830,"uid":289214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"已考水喉中工<br />\n遲D學揸巴士<br />\n可能會學驗樓，揸鏟車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:19:22.000Z","msg":"你係香港考定水喉中工？<br />\n但去到外國需唔需要重新考過？"},{"pid":"6118663c36cb44c44967bfa25a0a93b505b73c37","tid":2496830,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b28e8a632823076e28f06004d5d71f356c16109","tid":2496830,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bdf420273e1fd595219866e059a3c15cf15f288","tid":2496830,"uid":289214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"已考水喉中工<br />\n遲D學揸巴士<br />\n可能會學驗樓，揸鏟車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:19:22.000Z","msg":"你係香港考定水喉中工？<br />\n但去到外國需唔需要重新考過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"睇過，水喉中工無得直接COPY，如果真係做預左要讀 / 考過，但叫做有D興趣同讀過會熟識D<br />\n<br />\n香港讀電英國可以認証，但香港考個A牌要兩三年"},{"pid":"7506ae70c1739f75dee8d765d368068810e40c99","tid":2496830,"uid":289214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"英國做水電工有甚麼法例，牌照要留意<br />\n英國暫時只承認澳洲、加拿大、紐西蘭、愛爾蘭、南非和美國的電工牌照， 其他國家人士都要修讀指定課程或透過學徒訓練再經過評核先可以成為英國合資格電工。但如果你是香港的註冊電業工程人員， 便可透過另一種評估方法成為合資格電工Experienced Worker Assessment&rsquo;(EWA)。<br />\n<br />\n2020年7月英國對持有外國電力工作經驗的人士有推出新措拖- Experienced Worker Assessment&rsquo;(EWA)， 申請人需填寫一份技能評估表格(Skills Scan)和製作一份個人經驗資料夾，之後再做實務評核， 實務評核分為6個部份：<br />\n<br />\nSection A1:安全及風險評估-45分鐘<br />\n<br />\nSection A:綜合安裝-10小時<br />\n<br />\nSection B:檢測、測試和認證的-3.5小時<br />\n<br />\nSection C:安全處理<br />\n<br />\nSection D:故障檢查及修正-2小時<br />\n<br />\nSection E:應用已有相關知識-1小時<br />\n<br />\n在英國從事一般水喉潔具工作都是不需要特定牌照， 在英國你可以在當地修讀一些課程增強自己在水務工作上的實力， 例如City &amp; Guilds-Pluming Studies。當然你可以報讀專業課程， 加入專業學會協助你拓展人脈。"},{"pid":"ca310f2ed9e52be5fd483d511934d198d2abadf0","tid":2496830,"uid":232250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab6ff5ad210b286f70db03fb1175b9523ea57b03","tid":2496830,"uid":193220,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"點睇City &amp; Guilds 咖啡證書 ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"睇YouTube 好似係三個學啡之一<br />\n1.  erb <br />\n2. city &amp; guilds<br />\n3, sca <br />\n你講依個,價錢應該係中間，最貴係sca<br />\n我都想學，但屋企冇個d 咖啡機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利： 四五個月後閃"},{"pid":"a5b46863e4b7e117595bbb6b055cb58b19bab49c","tid":2496830,"uid":252437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:32:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1f47fa9397327c42a5fc79c9bc1f1c2068ac016e","tid":2496830,"uid":62837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1df5b7381d538c268ff106e1ba4c40e16f9479e9","tid":2496830,"uid":98473,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"a7b5beb4e709518caae34a5782e25d1cc53d334d","tid":2496830,"uid":127575,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:48:41.000Z","msg":"水電牌<br />\n咖啡證書"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05